on cooperation between the Chinese Writers' Association and the
Damascus-based Arab Writers' Union for the next three years.
</P>
<P>
The agreement stipulates the exchange of visits by writers, the
organization of intellectual meetings and discussions and exchange
of views on the literary works of either side with the object of
learning more about one another and enhancing bilateral bonds of
friendship.
</P>
<P>
It also stipulates the exchange of literary magazines and
selections of modern works of literature.
</P>
