<P>
As well as Tomba, the authorities are investigating his father
Franco, who is the sole director of New Events, Paolo Comellini,
Tomba's former business manager, and Luciano Bindini, who owns an
advertising agency linked to Comellini.
</P>
<P>
A tax official, Giuseppe Moscuzza, is meanwhile under
investigation for an alleged breach of confidentiality.
</P>
<P>
Tomba will only be questioned once the authorities have sifted
through documents, computers and floppy disks found at New Events
offices.
</P>
<P>
State prosecutor Enrico Cieri is investigating whether any of
Tomba's publicity contracts with sponsors were settled by
payments to foreign bank accounts.
</P>
<P>
Investigators have also sought advice from the Italian Ski
Federation over the nature of athletes' sponsorship contracts.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
