number of major corruption cases as part of the anti-corruption
drive.
</P>
<P>
"The focus of the anti-corruption work at present is the clues
we have in a number of major cases, which are to be dealt with in
a short time," said Hou Zongbin, a deputy secretary of the CCDI.
</P>
