that corruption remains serious in the country and the task of
combating it is a difficult one. He emphasized the importance of
co-ordinating the work of different government departments and
Party offices in battling corruption, and of establishing highly
qualified anti-corruption task forces with upright personnel.
</P>
<P>
Central and local officials, and military leaders attended
today's conference. 
