aroused attention from around the world and will have a profound
influence on the international community, Wang said.
</P>
<P>
He noted that after the return, the Chinese government will
practice the "one country, two systems" principle in Hong Kong,
which will enable Hong Kong to maintain prosperity and stability
and ensure it a rosy future.
</P>
