<HEADLINE> New Constituent Stock for Hang Seng China Enterprises Index </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, June 10 (Xinhua) -- Hang Seng Index Services Limited
today announced that Jiangxi Copper Company Limited, to be listed
on the Stock Exchange of Hong Kong on June 12, will be included as
a constituent stock of the Hang Seng China Enterprises Index
(HSCEI).
</P>
<P>
With the addition of Jiangxi Copper Company Limited, there will
be 29 constituent stocks in the HSCEI. The inclusion is in line
