Creative 50 led the gainers of the day as it rose by 1.1
Singapore dollars to finish at 24.2 dollars. NBT, SGM and the
Singapore Airlines increased by 20 cents each to end at 20.4
Singapore dollars, 1.1 Hong Kong dollars, and 12.5 Singapore
dollars respectively.
</P>
<P>
On the downside, JMH 400 was the biggest loser as it declined
by 80 cents to end at 7.25 US dollars. Local car distributor Cycle
&AMP; Carriage (C&AMP;C) fell by 40 cents to close at 14.1 Singapore
dollars, while ERL finished 35 cents lower at 2.28 dollars.
</P>
