of the Standing Committee of China's National People's Congress
Cheng Siyuan, Vice-Chairwoman of the National Committee of the
Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference He Luli,
Vice-Minister of Internal Trade Luo Zhiling who is accompanying
Thuwainy on the trip, and Chinese Ambassador to Oman Wang
Xiaozhuang, as well as Omani Secretary-General of the Foreign
Ministry, Minister of Agriculture and Fisheries, Secretary-General
of the Cabinet, Minister of Water Resources, and Minister of
Industry and Commerce.  
</P>
