the government forces have been sent to the Anuradhapura Hospital
but no casualty figures were available.
</P>
<P>
More than 400 LTTE rebels launched the attack against
government troops north of Notchchimottai in Vavuniya District.
But there were no further details of casualties, they said.
</P>
<P>
The LTTE has been fighting a 14-year guerrilla war against the
government for a separate state in the northeast of the country.
