<HEADLINE> Shanghai Sets up Telecommunications Service Company </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, June 10 (Xinhua) -- Cosmopolitan Shanghai has set up
a telecommunications service company to manage the electronic and
